1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:24,830 --> 00:01:28,950
[The Fearless Season 1]

3
00:01:29,220 --> 00:01:31,820
[Episode 34]

4
00:01:33,740 --> 00:01:35,830
Xia Shu, you stay here.

5
00:01:35,910 --> 00:01:38,750
I need to talk with Ms. Qiu in private.

6
00:01:47,110 --> 00:01:48,030
Hua,

7
00:01:48,750 --> 00:01:50,550
even though we hate it,

8
00:01:50,640 --> 00:01:52,070
we'd better act like we don't.

9
00:01:53,190 --> 00:01:54,630
Wipe that look off your face.

10
00:01:54,650 --> 00:01:55,630
You brought her on board

11
00:01:55,630 --> 00:01:56,590
without even discussing it with me.

12
00:01:56,610 --> 00:01:58,120
I called you out now.

13
00:01:58,590 --> 00:02:00,510
Besides, Fang Lihong called me.

14
00:02:00,950 --> 00:02:01,770
How could I say no?

15
00:02:01,790 --> 00:02:02,920
You teach me how to say no.

16
00:02:04,350 --> 00:02:05,950
Even if you have prejudice against Xia Shu,

17
00:02:05,950 --> 00:02:06,590
you have to admit

18
00:02:06,590 --> 00:02:08,110
that she may come across as a little silly,

19
00:02:08,110 --> 00:02:09,229
but she's not a bad person.

20
00:02:09,289 --> 00:02:10,350
I have no prejudice against her.

21
00:02:10,350 --> 00:02:11,990
I just instinctively dislike her.

22
00:02:13,310 --> 00:02:13,910
Besides,

23
00:02:13,950 --> 00:02:16,130
it's understandable that we had to fawn over her every day

24
00:02:16,160 --> 00:02:18,370
if we worked under her father.

25
00:02:18,670 --> 00:02:19,430
The point is that we are in a firm

26
00:02:19,430 --> 00:02:21,430
that requires us to fight with our abilities.

27
00:02:21,990 --> 00:02:22,600
Do we need someone

28
00:02:22,620 --> 00:02:24,450
who has nothing to offer but a good father?

29
00:02:25,240 --> 00:02:26,350
She has nothing to offer?

30
00:02:26,750 --> 00:02:28,790
If she was good at nothing, how did she earn her degree in the US

31
00:02:28,829 --> 00:02:30,990
and pass the Chinese bar exam?

32
00:02:31,560 --> 00:02:32,260
Besides,

33
00:02:32,550 --> 00:02:33,270
it's not a bad thing for us

34
00:02:33,270 --> 00:02:34,670
that she has a father in a higher position.

35
00:02:34,860 --> 00:02:36,860
Maybe he can bring us some cases in the future.

36
00:02:37,460 --> 00:02:37,940
Right?

37
00:02:38,390 --> 00:02:40,160
Qiu Hua, what I mean is

38
00:02:40,270 --> 00:02:41,550
that I'd rather

39
00:02:41,550 --> 00:02:43,110
have a simple-minded person

40
00:02:43,150 --> 00:02:44,350
than a bad guy.

41
00:02:45,000 --> 00:02:45,990
Let's take her.

42
00:02:46,910 --> 00:02:47,760
Pay more attention to her

43
00:02:47,870 --> 00:02:49,390
so that she won't get us into trouble.

44
00:02:49,980 --> 00:02:51,630
I also have to be a kindergarten teacher now?

45
00:02:52,110 --> 00:02:53,350
Alright? Let's go.

46
00:02:53,550 --> 00:02:54,280
I'll get some water.

47
00:02:54,510 --> 00:02:56,110
No. Give her this one.

48
00:02:56,110 --> 00:02:57,180
Say...

49
00:02:57,270 --> 00:02:58,780
something to her first.

50
00:03:03,990 --> 00:03:04,670
Xia Shu.

51
00:03:04,870 --> 00:03:05,800
Last time,

52
00:03:05,800 --> 00:03:07,110
you caused us such big trouble,

53
00:03:07,230 --> 00:03:09,110
but Qiu decided to let bygones be bygones

54
00:03:09,460 --> 00:03:10,880
and agreed to let you join us.

55
00:03:11,190 --> 00:03:12,320
Thank you, Sister Qiu Hua.

56
00:03:12,610 --> 00:03:14,490
Don't. You're a partner.

57
00:03:14,780 --> 00:03:15,550
It is an honor for us

58
00:03:15,550 --> 00:03:16,590
to have you join us.

59
00:03:16,610 --> 00:03:17,610
You think highly of us.

60
00:03:17,829 --> 00:03:18,670
We should thank each other.

61
00:03:18,670 --> 00:03:19,350
Thank each other.

62
00:03:19,990 --> 00:03:22,110
It's almost time. Ma Lili should be here soon.

63
00:03:22,980 --> 00:03:23,980
I'll get a glass of water first.

64
00:03:24,980 --> 00:03:25,820
Let me do it.

65
00:03:25,870 --> 00:03:26,960
Bring me a cup of Americano.

66
00:03:26,980 --> 00:03:27,570
Okay.

67
00:03:28,350 --> 00:03:29,230
She has advantages.

68
00:03:29,510 --> 00:03:30,270
At least, she runs fast.

69
00:03:38,980 --> 00:03:39,650
Mrs. Ma.

70
00:03:40,060 --> 00:03:41,340
Mrs. Luo, Ms. Qiu.

71
00:03:41,820 --> 00:03:44,180
This is another lawyer in our firm, Xia Shu.

72
00:03:44,200 --> 00:03:44,700
Hello.

73
00:03:44,829 --> 00:03:45,550
Hello.

74
00:03:45,980 --> 00:03:46,670
Mrs. Ma.

75
00:03:47,140 --> 00:03:48,780
Xu Jianshe's case has been remanded for retrial.

76
00:03:49,500 --> 00:03:51,850
What does "remanded for retrial" mean?

77
00:03:52,270 --> 00:03:54,270
It means that if the higher judicial organ determines

78
00:03:54,270 --> 00:03:56,550
that the facts of a case are unclear or that there is insufficient evidence,

79
00:03:56,710 --> 00:03:58,960
they'll remand the case to the original judicial organ for a new trial.

80
00:03:58,960 --> 00:04:00,390
That is its meaning.

81
00:04:00,770 --> 00:04:01,570
If

82
00:04:01,730 --> 00:04:03,930
they don't have any new evidence to add,

83
00:04:04,710 --> 00:04:06,870
there's a high chance that the original sentence will be changed in the retrial.

84
00:04:07,550 --> 00:04:08,270
Mrs. Ma,

85
00:04:08,430 --> 00:04:11,070
this case has gone on for so long.

86
00:04:11,400 --> 00:04:12,830
I don't think

87
00:04:12,860 --> 00:04:15,350
there will be any new evidence.

88
00:04:15,590 --> 00:04:16,670
No, no.

89
00:04:16,990 --> 00:04:18,990
You have no idea how many times they've investigated before.

90
00:04:19,060 --> 00:04:20,300
How could it not?

91
00:04:20,890 --> 00:04:23,070
Isn't there evidence of a debt dispute

92
00:04:23,090 --> 00:04:24,970
between Xu Jianshe and the victim?

93
00:04:25,080 --> 00:04:28,210
But I think that the case was remanded for retrial

94
00:04:28,230 --> 00:04:29,390
mainly because they believe

95
00:04:29,590 --> 00:04:31,510
that Xu Jianshe is not the main culprit in this case.

96
00:04:31,890 --> 00:04:33,370
As for the IOU,

97
00:04:33,430 --> 00:04:35,630
it shouldn't have much impact on the basic facts.

98
00:04:36,090 --> 00:04:36,500
Right.

99
00:04:36,530 --> 00:04:38,550
The verdict of the second trial is based on the process of the crime,

100
00:04:38,550 --> 00:04:39,909
not the motive.

101
00:04:40,360 --> 00:04:41,690
It's okay. Anyway,

102
00:04:41,720 --> 00:04:43,840
we finally took a small step forward.

103
00:04:44,150 --> 00:04:44,790
Mrs. Ma,

104
00:04:45,150 --> 00:04:47,470
I heard that you and Xu Jianshe are divorced.

105
00:04:47,670 --> 00:04:48,670
Right.

106
00:04:49,030 --> 00:04:49,710
Gosh.

107
00:04:49,860 --> 00:04:51,210
I believe in love again.

108
00:04:52,550 --> 00:04:53,350
Miss Xia.

109
00:04:54,370 --> 00:04:57,490
Xia Shu, why don't you sit there

110
00:04:57,510 --> 00:04:59,390
and take some notes?

111
00:05:06,590 --> 00:05:07,350
Mrs. Ma.

112
00:05:07,800 --> 00:05:09,720
We didn't let you down

113
00:05:09,740 --> 00:05:10,670
during the second trial.

114
00:05:11,150 --> 00:05:13,150
The second trial is now complete.

115
00:05:13,670 --> 00:05:15,590
You need to remit the remaining 150,000 yuan

116
00:05:15,590 --> 00:05:17,350
to our law firm as soon as possible.

117
00:05:17,390 --> 00:05:17,990
Okay.

118
00:05:18,110 --> 00:05:18,910
Don't worry.

119
00:05:19,150 --> 00:05:20,150
I'll raise it.

120
00:05:20,910 --> 00:05:23,580
Then, we might need to prepare for the retrial.

121
00:05:24,390 --> 00:05:27,150
Are you still going to let us represent you in this retrial?

122
00:05:27,670 --> 00:05:28,590
Of course.

123
00:05:28,910 --> 00:05:31,030
Of course, I have to count on you two.

124
00:05:31,270 --> 00:05:33,230
This retrial could be Xu Jianshe's only chance

125
00:05:33,360 --> 00:05:35,310
to regain his freedom

126
00:05:35,350 --> 00:05:37,230
or have his sentence reduced.

127
00:05:37,590 --> 00:05:39,710
The difficulty of defending him is obvious.

128
00:05:40,150 --> 00:05:41,640
So, if you and Mr. Xu

129
00:05:41,670 --> 00:05:43,230
want to continue hiring us,

130
00:05:43,470 --> 00:05:45,790
we need an additional 500,000 yuan for legal fees.

131
00:05:45,920 --> 00:05:47,140
You can pay 200,000 yuan first.

132
00:05:47,470 --> 00:05:49,670
You can pay the remaining amount in a lump sum

133
00:05:49,670 --> 00:05:50,830
after the results are announced.

134
00:05:52,830 --> 00:05:53,909
Okay. Got it.

135
00:05:56,060 --> 00:05:56,770
By the way,

136
00:05:57,340 --> 00:05:59,130
are you still going to visit Jianshe?

137
00:06:00,150 --> 00:06:01,760
If you choose not to retain us

138
00:06:01,790 --> 00:06:04,840
as your legal representation for the retrial,

139
00:06:05,140 --> 00:06:06,540
perhaps

140
00:06:07,710 --> 00:06:09,330
we will have one final opportunity to visit him

141
00:06:09,630 --> 00:06:12,550
to inform him of the outcome of the second trial.

142
00:06:13,110 --> 00:06:15,540
But if you continue hiring us,

143
00:06:15,990 --> 00:06:17,910
we'll have many chances to see him

144
00:06:18,150 --> 00:06:19,790
before the retrial.

145
00:06:23,050 --> 00:06:24,290
I may need your help

146
00:06:24,310 --> 00:06:25,770
with something.

147
00:06:26,590 --> 00:06:29,110
Can you ask him

148
00:06:29,710 --> 00:06:30,830
to sign the power of attorney

149
00:06:30,830 --> 00:06:32,560
that I gave you last time?

150
00:06:33,350 --> 00:06:35,270
So that I can help him sell the houses

151
00:06:35,470 --> 00:06:37,230
and pay the legal fees.

152
00:06:37,470 --> 00:06:38,150
No.

153
00:06:40,030 --> 00:06:41,670
This is against the law.

154
00:06:42,470 --> 00:06:44,350
We can only do it under one circumstance.

155
00:06:45,270 --> 00:06:46,350
What circumstance?

156
00:06:46,390 --> 00:06:49,230
Only when Xu Jianshe agrees to compensate the victim's family,

157
00:06:49,470 --> 00:06:50,790
with the judge's permission,

158
00:06:50,790 --> 00:06:52,909
can we get him to sign the power of attorney

159
00:06:53,030 --> 00:06:55,230
authorizing you to handle his property.

160
00:06:55,480 --> 00:06:56,450
But Ms. Qiu,

161
00:06:56,909 --> 00:06:58,670
we don't even know

162
00:06:58,670 --> 00:06:59,680
if Xu Jianshe is the one who killed him.

163
00:06:59,790 --> 00:07:00,830
Why should we compensate him?

164
00:07:01,230 --> 00:07:01,910
Besides,

165
00:07:02,130 --> 00:07:03,770
you've never seen that family.

166
00:07:03,830 --> 00:07:05,150
They have a big appetite.

167
00:07:05,290 --> 00:07:05,870
If they knew

168
00:07:05,890 --> 00:07:07,590
that Jianshe owned several houses,

169
00:07:07,590 --> 00:07:09,790
they wouldn't stop until they got all of them.

170
00:07:09,840 --> 00:07:10,640
I'm sorry.

171
00:07:10,940 --> 00:07:12,310
We can't do this.

172
00:07:13,120 --> 00:07:15,340
We're going to ask him to sign the agency agreement anyway.

173
00:07:15,370 --> 00:07:16,920
I don't think there is a problem with asking him to sign...

174
00:07:21,390 --> 00:07:22,030
Mrs. Ma,

175
00:07:22,670 --> 00:07:24,550
we've talked about this power of attorney

176
00:07:24,990 --> 00:07:26,790
many times.

177
00:07:27,410 --> 00:07:30,320
Now, we really don't have much time.

178
00:07:30,590 --> 00:07:31,910
For the retrial,

179
00:07:32,270 --> 00:07:32,990
we shouldn't

180
00:07:32,990 --> 00:07:34,909
waste our time on this matter.

181
00:07:35,230 --> 00:07:37,210
If you really want him to sign it,

182
00:07:37,260 --> 00:07:39,570
it can only be under the condition that Ms. Qiu just mentioned.

183
00:07:39,730 --> 00:07:40,840
There is no other way.

184
00:07:41,230 --> 00:07:42,830
I'll think about it when I go back.

185
00:07:44,590 --> 00:07:45,590
If there's nothing else,

186
00:07:45,590 --> 00:07:46,909
I'll go now.

187
00:07:47,110 --> 00:07:48,110
Thank you.

188
00:07:48,780 --> 00:07:49,580
Thank you.

189
00:07:50,909 --> 00:07:51,909
I have to go.

190
00:07:52,000 --> 00:07:53,230
We're still very happy about the outcome.

191
00:07:55,710 --> 00:07:56,470
No need to see me off.

192
00:07:56,470 --> 00:07:57,230
It's okay. Let's go.

193
00:07:58,980 --> 00:08:00,470
This woman is so amazing.

194
00:08:01,910 --> 00:08:03,030
What's so great about her?

195
00:08:03,630 --> 00:08:05,830
She's willing to risk everything to save her ex-husband.

196
00:08:05,990 --> 00:08:07,150
I wouldn't be able to do that if I were her.

197
00:08:07,190 --> 00:08:08,750
If something like this happened to my boyfriend,

198
00:08:08,780 --> 00:08:09,780
I'd have run the hell away a long time ago.

199
00:08:10,590 --> 00:08:12,800
You'd better hope you never encounter this kind of situation in your life.

200
00:08:13,510 --> 00:08:17,530
[Jingbei Court]

201
00:08:24,350 --> 00:08:25,020
What do you think

202
00:08:25,030 --> 00:08:26,320
the judge

203
00:08:26,350 --> 00:08:27,720
wants to see us now?

204
00:08:27,950 --> 00:08:29,550
I don't think there's anything important.

205
00:08:29,750 --> 00:08:31,520
The judge definitely hopes

206
00:08:31,550 --> 00:08:33,350
we can persuade Xu Jianshe.

207
00:08:33,510 --> 00:08:34,909
I think it's nearly impossible for us to win

208
00:08:34,940 --> 00:08:36,289
if we plead not guilty in this case.

209
00:08:36,760 --> 00:08:38,470
We can only hope that Xu Jianshe's sentence will be reduced.

210
00:08:38,830 --> 00:08:39,830
But for some reason,

211
00:08:39,830 --> 00:08:41,350
I just believe that he's innocent.

212
00:08:41,380 --> 00:08:42,860
I think you believe in Ma Lili, right?

213
00:08:42,990 --> 00:08:43,830
Yes.

214
00:08:43,990 --> 00:08:44,870
How many people in this world

215
00:08:44,890 --> 00:08:46,250
can be like Ma Lili?

216
00:08:47,220 --> 00:08:48,310
Look at Xia Shu.

217
00:08:48,460 --> 00:08:50,340
Suddenly, she seems to see through humanity.

218
00:08:50,700 --> 00:08:51,710
Well.

219
00:08:57,510 --> 00:08:59,520
Are you Xu Jianshe's attorneys?

220
00:09:00,110 --> 00:09:00,950
Yes, we are.

221
00:09:01,150 --> 00:09:01,900
My surname is Wei.

222
00:09:02,390 --> 00:09:04,030
I'm the person in charge of this case.

223
00:09:04,510 --> 00:09:07,220
I've studied all the materials about this case.

224
00:09:07,470 --> 00:09:08,590
There is no problem

225
00:09:08,850 --> 00:09:11,960
convicting Xu Jianshe.

226
00:09:12,650 --> 00:09:15,170
The final sentence of another co-defendant

227
00:09:15,200 --> 00:09:16,430
won't be as severe either.

228
00:09:16,960 --> 00:09:18,670
It has something to do

229
00:09:18,700 --> 00:09:20,420
with his proactive compensation

230
00:09:20,460 --> 00:09:21,640
and getting an understanding of the victim's family.

231
00:09:21,830 --> 00:09:22,590
Well.

232
00:09:22,670 --> 00:09:25,750
Is it necessary to convince Xu Jianshe to negotiate compensation
with the victim's family?

233
00:09:26,230 --> 00:09:27,110
As far as I know,

234
00:09:27,190 --> 00:09:28,240
Xu Jianshe

235
00:09:28,400 --> 00:09:30,420
is capable of providing compensation.

236
00:09:30,550 --> 00:09:32,590
Once he gets forgiveness from the victim's family,

237
00:09:32,800 --> 00:09:35,080
it can also alleviate the conflict between the two parties.

238
00:09:35,350 --> 00:09:36,230
What do you think?

239
00:09:38,560 --> 00:09:40,020
Judge Wei, let's discuss it.

240
00:09:40,050 --> 00:09:41,590
We'll give you our final decision later.

241
00:09:41,590 --> 00:09:42,350
Is that okay?

242
00:09:42,470 --> 00:09:42,830
Okay.

243
00:09:43,230 --> 00:09:44,230
Here is my office.

244
00:09:44,260 --> 00:09:45,010
Okay, thank you.

245
00:09:50,060 --> 00:09:52,310
What do you think we should do next?

246
00:09:52,550 --> 00:09:54,000
Xia Shu, you're not involved in those two trials,

247
00:09:54,030 --> 00:09:54,980
so you have no right to speak.

248
00:09:56,090 --> 00:09:57,830
I think the judge's suggestion is good.

249
00:09:58,510 --> 00:10:00,740
She mentioned the sentencing of the co-defendant.

250
00:10:01,140 --> 00:10:03,660
Does it mean that if Xu Jianshe actively compensates the victim,

251
00:10:03,680 --> 00:10:05,930
he will also receive a lenient sentence, right?

252
00:10:05,960 --> 00:10:07,040
I agree with you.

253
00:10:07,650 --> 00:10:10,530
That's how we reply to Judge Wei.

254
00:10:11,060 --> 00:10:12,440
Then we go visit Xu Jianshe.

255
00:10:14,220 --> 00:10:14,940
But

256
00:10:14,980 --> 00:10:16,890
only if he pleads guilty

257
00:10:16,990 --> 00:10:18,190
and actively compensates the victim's family.

258
00:10:20,560 --> 00:10:22,630
What if he disagrees?

259
00:10:23,170 --> 00:10:25,080
We can explain the pros and cons to him.

260
00:10:26,630 --> 00:10:28,990
I always think Xu Jianshe is so determined

261
00:10:29,010 --> 00:10:31,590
because someone has been giving him the wrong information.

262
00:10:32,830 --> 00:10:34,240
But after we took over,

263
00:10:34,640 --> 00:10:35,350
he wouldn't have any contact

264
00:10:35,350 --> 00:10:37,310
with the outside world.

265
00:10:37,710 --> 00:10:39,470
It won't be as hard as it used to be to persuade him.

266
00:10:39,500 --> 00:10:40,490
We can give it a try.

267
00:10:42,000 --> 00:10:42,510
Okay.

268
00:10:47,000 --> 00:10:49,840
[Detention Center]

269
00:10:51,750 --> 00:10:52,990
Come to Meeting Room 5.

270
00:10:55,680 --> 00:10:56,400
By the way, Xia Shu,

271
00:10:56,790 --> 00:10:58,070
you have to wait for us here.

272
00:10:58,110 --> 00:10:59,640
About your Agent Agreement,

273
00:10:59,710 --> 00:11:01,190
we'll ask Xu Jianshe to sign it

274
00:11:01,210 --> 00:11:02,370
after we meet him.

275
00:11:02,710 --> 00:11:03,590
-Don’t worry. -Okay.

276
00:11:16,510 --> 00:11:17,230
Mr. Xu.

277
00:11:17,640 --> 00:11:18,730
We've been unable to find

278
00:11:19,100 --> 00:11:21,310
any evidence to prove your innocence in your case.

279
00:11:21,630 --> 00:11:24,600
