307
00:13:06,350 --> 00:13:07,870
So we advise you again to consider

308
00:13:07,870 --> 00:13:11,020
pleading for a misdemeanor and negotiating the compensation.

309
00:13:11,230 --> 00:13:14,060
I think we can

310
