332
00:14:13,430 --> 00:14:14,310
Of course.

333
00:14:14,870 --> 00:14:18,350
The date for your retrial will be set soon.

334
00:14:19,150 --> 00:14:21,310
We'll come to visit you next week.

335
00:14:21,630 --> 00:14:22,350
You can

336
00:14:22,350 --> 00:14:24,180
