434
00:18:13,470 --> 00:18:16,790
Is our small counseling room available?

435
00:18:18,550 --> 00:18:19,030
Okay.

436
00:18:19,290 --> 00:18:20,830
Bring her here.

437
00:18:21,030 --> 00:18:22,140
Okay, thank you.

