00:18:37,540 --> 00:18:38,050
Have a seat.

442
00:18:42,370 --> 00:18:43,050
Here's the thing.

443
00:18:43,790 --> 00:18:45,470
I want you to be my lawyer

444
00:18:45,620 --> 00:18:46,640
