Everyone in the lobby saw it.

566
00:23:00,450 --> 00:23:01,530
This will be fun.

567
00:23:02,870 --> 00:23:06,550
The lawyer from our Liangcheng firm was handcuffed by the police.

568
00:23:06,980 --> 00:23:08,040
Do you know why?

569
00:23:08,830 --> 00:23:09,870
What else could it be?

570
00:23:10,380 --> 00:23:11,900
Maybe it's because of

571
00:23:11,930 --> 00:23:13,360
that remanded case she's handling.

572
00:23:14,190 --> 00:23:15,360
Luo Yingzi

573
00:23:15,390 --> 00:23:16,630
is too bold.

574
00:23:16,650 --> 00:23:18,300
She can do anything.

575
00:23:19,310 --> 00:23:21,470
She might have bribed the judge in the second trial.

576
00:23:22,060 --> 00:23:22,660
We can't keep

577
00:23:23,220 --> 00:23:25,100
this kind of person in our firm.

578
00:23:26,090 --> 00:23:27,850
Now she has a criminal record.

579
00:23:28,040 --> 00:23:29,320
She can't be a lawyer.

580
00:23:29,880 --> 00:23:31,720
If we were to keep a lawyer like her

581
00:23:31,990 --> 00:23:34,420
what'd we look like in the legal world?

582
00:23:38,920 --> 00:23:40,560
Ms. Qiu, bad news.

583
00:23:40,670 --> 00:23:41,270
What's wrong?

584
00:23:41,290 --> 00:23:42,730
Mrs. Luo was arrested by the police.

585
00:23:44,470 --> 00:23:45,710
Do you know why?

586
00:23:45,730 --> 00:23:48,140
I heard from a police officer that she is suspected of fraud.

587
00:23:48,340 --> 00:23:49,620
How is that possible?

588
00:23:50,110 --> 00:23:51,480
They must have caught the wrong person.

589
00:23:51,880 --> 00:23:53,200
Should we go to the police station

590
00:23:53,230 --> 00:23:53,940
and get her out now?

591
00:23:54,070 --> 00:23:55,430
You're not helping.

592
00:23:55,560 --> 00:23:57,880
The police can only determine the specific reason
after it has been investigated.

593
00:23:58,550 --> 00:23:59,750
Did Mrs. Luo say anything

594
00:23:59,750 --> 00:24:00,710
when she was taken away?

595
00:24:00,730 --> 00:24:03,050
She said that she wanted you to be her attorney.

596
00:24:06,290 --> 00:24:07,130
Well, Mr. Tao,

597
00:24:07,580 --> 00:24:08,340
please excuse us.

598
00:24:08,400 --> 00:24:09,570
I want to talk to Han privately.

599
00:24:09,680 --> 00:24:10,250
Okay.

600
00:24:18,840 --> 00:24:19,550
Han.

601
00:24:21,030 --> 00:24:22,320
Luo Yingzi

602
00:24:22,350 --> 00:24:24,240
has evidence of your sexual harassment.

603
00:24:24,490 --> 00:24:25,360
Don't forget.

604
00:24:26,710 --> 00:24:28,190
In the future, when she gets out,

605
00:24:28,790 --> 00:24:30,840
if she finds out that you were the one who insisted on firing her

606
00:24:31,420 --> 00:24:32,840
and she discloses the evidence,

607
00:24:33,640 --> 00:24:35,260
can you still be a lawyer?

608
00:24:38,340 --> 00:24:40,490
I'm doing this for the sake of our firm.

609
00:24:40,550 --> 00:24:41,830
For the firm?

610
00:24:41,870 --> 00:24:43,390
Then, don't gloat.

611
00:24:43,840 --> 00:24:44,600
You don't know the situation yet.

612
00:24:44,630 --> 00:24:46,030
Then you came here, talking nonsense.

613
00:24:47,210 --> 00:24:48,180
Anyway,

614
00:24:48,350 --> 00:24:49,470
she is our lawyer.

615
00:24:50,400 --> 00:24:51,320
We have to protect her.

616
00:24:51,550 --> 00:24:52,500
As for what will happen in the future,

617
00:24:52,610 --> 00:24:54,610
we'll talk about it later.

618
00:24:55,790 --> 00:24:57,250
Look how smug you are.

619
00:25:05,610 --> 00:25:06,200
Mr. Tao,

620
00:25:06,680 --> 00:25:07,670
come back.

621
00:25:07,860 --> 00:25:08,700
Let's discuss

622
00:25:08,720 --> 00:25:10,090
and see what to do about it.

623
00:25:14,620 --> 00:25:16,100
Do you want me to find out...

624
00:25:18,140 --> 00:25:19,350
why?

625
00:25:20,120 --> 00:25:21,110
No matter what,

626
00:25:21,140 --> 00:25:23,210
we must keep it a secret.

627
00:25:24,160 --> 00:25:26,350
After all, she is one of our lawyers.

628
00:25:26,790 --> 00:25:28,790
She was arrested in broad daylight.

629
00:25:28,810 --> 00:25:30,150
You can keep it a secret?

630
00:25:30,970 --> 00:25:32,380
Keep your mouth shut first.

631
00:25:33,540 --> 00:25:34,910
Han, let me tell you.

632
00:25:35,220 --> 00:25:37,220
If one day I find out that you are the one who leaked it,

633
00:25:37,600 --> 00:25:38,910
there will be consequences.

634
00:25:41,670 --> 00:25:42,500
Ms. Fang.

635
00:25:42,670 --> 00:25:44,810
Luo Yingzi was taken away by the police.

636
00:25:47,790 --> 00:25:48,510
How capable.

637
00:25:49,030 --> 00:25:50,500
She even got herself into the police station.

638
00:25:50,590 --> 00:25:52,420
Ms. Fang, we have to save her.

639
00:25:55,000 --> 00:25:55,940
It depends on

640
00:25:56,100 --> 00:25:57,340
what she did.

641
00:25:57,960 --> 00:26:00,190
If she really committed a crime,

642
00:26:00,380 --> 00:26:01,490
not even God could save her.

643
00:26:01,720 --> 00:26:03,790
Do you think Luo Yingzi could commit a crime?

644
00:26:03,880 --> 00:26:04,880
I can't say for sure.

645
00:26:05,880 --> 00:26:06,880
If you say so,

646
00:26:06,910 --> 00:26:07,990
you're being irresponsible

647
00:26:07,990 --> 00:26:08,930
to your client.

648
00:26:08,960 --> 00:26:10,960
Not to mention, Luo Yingzi would never commit a crime.

649
00:26:11,070 --> 00:26:12,440
Even if she did commit a crime,

650
00:26:12,460 --> 00:26:13,900
you are still her lawyer.

651
00:26:14,190 --> 00:26:16,430
You should also protect her legal rights.

652
00:26:16,510 --> 00:26:17,190
Ms. Fang,

653
00:26:17,390 --> 00:26:18,470
how could you say that?

654
00:26:18,800 --> 00:26:19,350
Qiu Hua.

655
00:26:19,540 --> 00:26:20,640
We will help her since she won't.

656
00:26:21,030 --> 00:26:22,320
Calm down.

657
00:26:22,460 --> 00:26:23,820
Ms. Fang just said it.

658
00:26:23,850 --> 00:26:25,370
We were discussing how to save her.

659
00:26:25,510 --> 00:26:26,150
Even if it isn't for her,

660
00:26:26,170 --> 00:26:27,840
we'll save her for the sake of our firm!

661
00:26:31,020 --> 00:26:31,720
Qiu Hua.

662
00:26:32,460 --> 00:26:34,450
Do you know why?

663
00:26:34,830 --> 00:26:36,840
They said she's suspected of fraud.

664
00:26:37,460 --> 00:26:38,210
Not bribery,

665
00:26:38,340 --> 00:26:39,290
but fraud.

666
00:26:40,540 --> 00:26:41,590
What do you mean by that?

667
00:26:43,070 --> 00:26:43,600
Han.

668
00:26:43,930 --> 00:26:45,520
You're done here.

669
00:26:45,540 --> 00:26:46,330
You can go now.

670
00:26:55,090 --> 00:26:55,740
Qiu Hua.

671
00:26:56,040 --> 00:26:58,640
You've been close to her.

672
00:26:58,990 --> 00:26:59,950
Think about it.

673
00:27:00,280 --> 00:27:02,160
What exactly is it

674
00:27:02,350 --> 00:27:04,900
that could make the police think she committed fraud?

675
00:27:05,090 --> 00:27:07,180
It should have something to do with her filing a police report

676
00:27:07,350 --> 00:27:08,920
about Liu Ming's fraud.

677
00:27:08,960 --> 00:27:11,370
Could it be that the police think she is the co-conspirator?

678
00:27:11,820 --> 00:27:13,240
There's no way Luo Yingzi would cheat for money.

679
00:27:13,330 --> 00:27:14,930
Someone must have set her up.

680
00:27:18,690 --> 00:27:21,320
If it's related to Liu Ming...

681
00:27:22,620 --> 00:27:24,380
I've been her divorce lawyer.

682
00:27:24,880 --> 00:27:25,850
Of course,

683
00:27:26,280 --> 00:27:27,680
I'm also her lawyer on this matter.

684
00:27:28,630 --> 00:27:29,670
Here, Qiu Hua,

685
00:27:30,000 --> 00:27:30,880
find out

686
00:27:30,970 --> 00:27:33,420
the reason for their investigation.

687
00:27:33,630 --> 00:27:34,100
Okay.

688
00:27:34,120 --> 00:27:35,200
I'm familiar with the police.

689
00:27:35,440 --> 00:27:35,870
I'll go.

690
00:27:36,990 --> 00:27:37,930
Thank you, Mr. Tao.

691
00:27:40,100 --> 00:27:41,740
Xia Shu, Qiu Hua.

692
00:27:43,990 --> 00:27:46,290
Da Zheng Firm is representing the bank.

693
00:27:46,470 --> 00:27:49,030
If it's about the bank loan,

694
00:27:49,320 --> 00:27:50,200
I believe

695
00:27:50,630 --> 00:27:52,340
the Da Zheng firm must be involved.

696
00:27:52,590 --> 00:27:54,600
The top priority for both of you is to find out

697
00:27:54,900 --> 00:27:56,780
who framed Luo Yingzi.

698
00:27:57,740 --> 00:27:59,060
Okay, we'll go now.

699
00:28:09,390 --> 00:28:10,890
You go to Da Zheng and ask.

700
00:28:10,910 --> 00:28:11,750
I'll go to the bank.

701
00:28:12,080 --> 00:28:12,890
Let’s split up.

702
00:28:12,920 --> 00:28:13,850
-Okay. -Call me if anything happens.

703
00:28:13,890 --> 00:28:14,330
Okay.

704
00:28:19,600 --> 00:28:21,880
I've always known that Luo Yingzi is a bad person.

705
00:28:23,200 --> 00:28:26,080
A lawyer was taken away by the police at our front door.

706
00:28:26,390 --> 00:28:27,870
How are we supposed to run our firm after that?

707
00:28:28,150 --> 00:28:29,750
But whom else does she respect?

708
00:28:30,280 --> 00:28:31,400
Whom else?

709
00:28:32,230 --> 00:28:33,440
She is still a young lawyer.

710
00:28:33,460 --> 00:28:35,640
But she has already walked all over us.

711
00:28:36,230 --> 00:28:38,730
Turns out, she won by breaking the law.

712
00:28:40,620 --> 00:28:41,830
Fortunately, something happened this time.

713
00:28:41,850 --> 00:28:43,730
Otherwise, there might be a greater problem in the future.

714
00:28:53,410 --> 00:28:54,800
Turnabout is fair play.

715
00:29:01,650 --> 00:29:02,580
Not good enough.

716
00:29:07,620 --> 00:29:08,340
Miss Zhang.

717
00:29:08,790 --> 00:29:10,470
A lady is looking for Mr. Chen.

718
00:29:18,430 --> 00:29:19,310
You are?

719
00:29:19,330 --> 00:29:20,440
Are you Zhang Shilan?

720
00:29:20,660 --> 00:29:22,870
I'm a colleague of Mrs. Luo from the Liangcheng firm.

721
00:29:22,910 --> 00:29:24,190
I'm looking for Mr. Chen. Is he here?

722
00:29:24,780 --> 00:29:25,850
He went to see a client.

723
00:29:26,710 --> 00:29:27,640
Does he know

724
00:29:27,640 --> 00:29:29,060
that Mrs. Luo has been taken away by the police?

725
00:29:30,790 --> 00:29:31,910
What did you say?

726
00:29:49,310 --> 00:29:50,410
Hello, Qiu Hua.

727
00:29:50,890 --> 00:29:51,620
Xia Shu.

728
00:29:51,880 --> 00:29:53,590
How did it go at Da Zheng?

729
00:29:54,480 --> 00:29:55,810
I didn't get to see Mr. Chen.

730
00:29:55,840 --> 00:29:57,160
I didn't find anything.

731
00:29:58,550 --> 00:29:59,950
I went to the bank.

732
00:30:00,040 --> 00:30:02,030
The bank manager doesn't want to see me at all.

733
00:30:02,590 --> 00:30:03,990
OK, keep checking.

734
00:30:04,440 --> 00:30:04,920
Okay.

735
00:30:10,520 --> 00:30:12,720
[Ma Lili]

736
00:30:13,320 --> 00:30:14,710
Hello, Mrs. Ma.

737
00:30:14,740 --> 00:30:15,740
What happened?

738
00:30:16,190 --> 00:30:16,990
Miss Xia,

739
00:30:17,140 --> 00:30:18,450
can we meet?

740
00:30:18,630 --> 00:30:19,840
I have something urgent to tell you.

741
00:30:20,410 --> 00:30:21,650
I'll send you the address.

742
00:30:23,600 --> 00:30:25,350
Okay, I'll come to you now.

743
00:30:54,580 --> 00:30:55,270
Luo Yingzi.

744
00:30:56,070 --> 00:30:57,110
We've received a report

745
00:30:57,190 --> 00:30:59,220
alleging that you and your husband are suspected of fraud.

746
00:30:59,950 --> 00:31:00,990
Tell us what happened.

747
00:31:01,700 --> 00:31:02,430
Officers,

748
00:31:03,620 --> 00:31:04,640
I'm a lawyer.

749
00:31:04,860 --> 00:31:05,740
I know the law too.

750
00:31:06,610 --> 00:31:08,570
It's not my husband and I who are involved in fraud,

751
00:31:08,600 --> 00:31:10,390
but my husband alone.

752
00:31:11,170 --> 00:31:13,510
I have nothing to do

753
00:31:13,530 --> 00:31:15,140
with my husband's involvement in defrauding a bank loan.

754
00:31:15,630 --> 00:31:16,830
I reported his fraud to the police

755
00:31:16,850 --> 00:31:18,560
a few days ago.

756
00:31:18,590 --> 00:31:20,380
You can check it out.

757
00:31:21,230 --> 00:31:21,900
You...

758
00:31:22,270 --> 00:31:23,440
I haven't finished yet.

759
00:31:23,570 --> 00:31:24,340
I'm sorry.

760
00:31:26,500 --> 00:31:27,630
Because I called the police,

761
00:31:28,190 --> 00:31:31,110
the bank can't auction the house

762
00:31:31,550 --> 00:31:33,030
to collect on their loan.

763
00:31:33,470 --> 00:31:34,470
So, they got anxious

764
00:31:35,150 --> 00:31:36,100
and sued me.

765
00:31:37,600 --> 00:31:38,240
I'm done.

766
00:31:39,030 --> 00:31:40,470
You'd better get up on the right side

767
00:31:40,520 --> 00:31:41,640
and think about it calmly.

768
00:31:42,060 --> 00:31:43,670
The bank provided not only physical evidence

769
00:31:44,400 --> 00:31:45,130
but also witnesses.

770
00:31:45,450 --> 00:31:47,130
If they have a witness, ask him to come out and meet me.

771
00:31:47,150 --> 00:31:48,240
We can confront each other.

772
00:31:49,550 --> 00:31:51,420
We can't just listen to the witness, can we?

773
00:31:58,800 --> 00:31:59,870
I want to see my lawyer.

774
00:32:00,490 --> 00:32:01,840
This is my legal right.

775
00:32:04,670 --> 00:32:05,670
Contact her lawyer for her.

776
00:32:19,900 --> 00:32:22,110
Shuo, why didn't you answer the phone?

777
00:32:22,140 --> 00:32:23,500
I was talking to a client.

778
00:32:23,810 --> 00:32:26,570
Someone from Liangcheng said that Yingzi had been arrested.

779
00:32:27,000 --> 00:32:27,840
Did that person say why?

780
00:32:28,770 --> 00:32:29,750
A bank fraud.

781
00:32:30,190 --> 00:32:32,160
She may have already been placed in criminal detention.

782
00:32:33,390 --> 00:32:34,150
I'll go with you.

783
00:32:34,170 --> 00:32:35,050
No need.

784
00:33:21,580 --> 00:33:22,140
Come in.

785
00:33:23,400 --> 00:33:24,130
Mr. Wang.

786
00:33:24,310 --> 00:33:25,070
It's me again.

787
00:33:26,420 --> 00:33:27,490
What are you doing here?

788
00:33:28,000 --> 00:33:29,240
I'm here to claim credit.

789
00:33:29,660 --> 00:33:30,490
What credit?

790
00:33:31,050 --> 00:33:31,660
May I sit?

791
00:33:31,780 --> 00:33:32,150
Sit.

792
00:33:36,150 --> 00:33:37,360
Luo Yingzi

793
00:33:37,380 --> 00:33:39,730
reported her husband's blackmail.

794
00:33:40,290 --> 00:33:41,070
Last time, you told me

795
00:33:41,090 --> 00:33:42,080
that it was a marital conspiracy,

796
00:33:42,120 --> 00:33:43,760
and I didn't believe it.

797
00:33:44,230 --> 00:33:44,670
Right?

798
00:33:45,600 --> 00:33:46,370
But later,

799
00:33:46,400 --> 00:33:47,710
I carefully thought about it.

800
00:33:48,040 --> 00:33:48,750
I think

801
00:33:48,940 --> 00:33:50,380
that, Mr. Wang, you have a point.

802
00:33:50,560 --> 00:33:51,070
Really.

803
00:33:51,940 --> 00:33:52,630
So,

804
00:33:52,860 --> 00:33:54,410
I secretly and casually

805
00:33:55,190 --> 00:33:56,480
told this news

806
00:33:56,500 --> 00:33:58,330
to my classmate,

807
00:33:58,590 --> 00:33:59,980
who works at the police station.

808
00:34:00,000 --> 00:34:00,960
Guess what?

809
00:34:01,120 --> 00:34:01,590
What?

810
00:34:02,540 --> 00:34:05,220
Luo Yingzi was arrested today.

811
00:34:08,800 --> 00:34:10,190
You used this trick too?

812
00:34:11,530 --> 00:34:13,000
Who else used it?

813
00:34:13,840 --> 00:34:14,719
To be honest,

814
00:34:14,960 --> 00:34:16,570
we also reported it to the police.

815
00:34:16,909 --> 00:34:18,679
Isn't it "great minds think alike"?

816
00:34:19,020 --> 00:34:20,900
It's not that we think alike.

817
00:34:20,960 --> 00:34:21,570
Don't forget.

818
00:34:21,949 --> 00:34:24,389
You taught us this move.

819
00:34:24,409 --> 00:34:25,690
Mr. Wang, here you go again.

820
00:34:25,710 --> 00:34:26,389
Again.

821
00:34:28,659 --> 00:34:29,969
Here is the thing.

822
00:34:31,710 --> 00:34:32,460
You called the police,

823
00:34:33,540 --> 00:34:34,510
and Luo Yingzi was arrested.

824
00:34:35,630 --> 00:34:37,480
Then let's make it a fact.

825
00:34:39,480 --> 00:34:40,320
Let's find evidence.

826
00:34:41,320 --> 00:34:42,650
We have evidence.

827
00:34:43,250 --> 00:34:46,159
She came to the bank back then with her husband.

828
00:34:46,690 --> 00:34:47,530
It can't be.

829
00:34:47,860 --> 00:34:48,659
She came with her husband,

830
00:34:48,679 --> 00:34:49,719
and then she reported it to the police.

831
00:34:49,840 --> 00:34:50,989
Is she stupid?

832
00:34:51,030 --> 00:34:52,590
We don't care.

833
00:34:53,230 --> 00:34:53,840
Anyway,

834
00:34:53,980 --> 00:34:56,110
her husband said that the woman was his wife.

835
00:35:00,950 --> 00:35:01,460
Mr. Wang.

836
00:35:02,000 --> 00:35:04,080
It's fine that you didn't care about this before.

837
00:35:04,860 --> 00:35:06,230
But now you've called the police.

838
00:35:06,250 --> 00:35:08,100
It's a lawsuit now.

839
00:35:08,130 --> 00:35:09,270
Then you have to consider it.

840
00:35:10,020 --> 00:35:11,330
How about this?

841
00:35:12,340 --> 00:35:13,360
I mean, if you can.

842
00:35:13,790 --> 00:35:15,030
If you can,

843
00:35:15,060 --> 00:35:16,330
let me have a look

844
00:35:16,360 --> 00:35:17,220
at the evidence you have.

845
00:35:17,800 --> 00:35:18,560
I'm a lawyer.

846
00:35:19,280 --> 00:35:20,280
I'll check it out for you.

847
00:35:20,300 --> 00:35:20,820
Let's see

848
00:35:20,850 --> 00:35:22,420
if we can avoid any risks.

849
